responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "2697B4A048BC44206E57279D22E9141B", "I don\'t know what the horn of doom is, but all I ever found was some marble coffin to the ruler of a defunct dynasty. His rule may be in the afterlife, but not his riches. There\'s probably enough gold in there to feed and arm a new empire. But those minos will never see it, not without the cantrip.")
